bio: Ian Harold is a 27-year-old lawyer who enjoys reading, glamping and cycling. He is friendly and bright, but can also be very greedy and a bit sneaky. He is a British Hindu who defines himself as bisexual. He has a degree in law. He is allergic to latex. Physically, Ian is slightly overweight but otherwise in good shape. He is average-height with walnut skin, black hair and black eyes.He grew up in a middle class neighbourhood. He was raised by his mother, his father having left when he was young...
name: Ian Hunter
